{"tid":605038,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"童子尿蛋防中暑 檔販：連湯喝更佳","createTime":"2018-03-25T09:45:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T09:46:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5cdf77e093d3460beefd1bd6f6eae7cbf0989e02","tid":605038,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:45:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180325/20342266\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180325%2F20342266&d=pA7LzFYulaAqKx0ipF9zebDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=0ffb0c5a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180325%2F20342266&h=913b7b3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180325/20342266</a><br />\n<br />\n童子尿蛋防中暑<br />\n檔販：連湯喝更佳<br />\n<br />\n兩岸要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180325/large/25cb5p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180325%2Flarge%2F25cb5p.jpg&h=2f8946c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n檔主將童子尿倒入雞蛋中。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這是春天的味道。踏入3月，浙江東陽市面就會傳來陣陣「飄香」，一股尿餲味瀰漫四周，原來當地流行在3月吃童子尿蛋，街邊許多攤檔正不停澆尿煮蛋叫賣鑊中即時蒸起一陣陣「尿煙」。有當地檔販說，吃了童尿蛋的人，夏天不容易中暑和犯睏，而且喝下「湯」效果更好。<br />\n<br />\n童子尿煮蛋，不僅是當地傳統美食，更在2008年獲選為當地非物質文化遺產。有賣童子尿蛋的店家豪言，一天能賣上300、400隻蛋。不過有外地人買來一試後，即撒手擰頭、皺起眉毛直呼「不吃了不吃了！味道太重！」<br />\n<br />\n而當地檔販製作童子尿蛋最重要的原料是尿，一般採用當地小學三年級或以下的健康男孩尿，店家會一般在幼兒園或小學收集男孩尿液。街頭販賣的是無添加的尿蛋，味道除了來自雞蛋本身，就都是尿的精華。<br />\n<br />\n梨視頻"},{"pid":"e3c828d1ac59258a38ab49e56383b666f52fbfe5","tid":605038,"uid":157193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:46:08.000Z","msg":"Cls睇見都想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}